source: Při potyčce, která vzbudila v centru města velkou pozornost a kvůli které muselo na místě zasahovat několik policejních hlídek i strážníků, šlo o rodinné spory.
reference: At the stick, which aroused great attention in the city centre and for which several police patrols and constables had to intervene on the spot, it was a family feud.
translation: The skirmish, which attracted a lot of attention in the city centre as several police units had to intervene at the scene, was the result of a family dispute.
